               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 3r-153v)
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of
                     David” (fols. 3r-127r)
 I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt “The Canticles of the
                     Prophets” (fols. 127r-137v)
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs” (fols.
                     137v-143r)
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 143va-150vb)
                     I-5) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (150vb-153vb)
 
 Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
